This project is licensed under the MIT License.

The 1.58-bit quantization is heavily inspired by [The Era of 1-bit LLMs](https://arxiv.org/abs/2402.17764) (Microsoft) and the BitNet architecture.

The Masked Diffusion implementation is inspired by recent advances in Discrete Diffusion models for sequence generation.
